<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>RowGateway objects behave inconsistently if you set values using object property style ($object-&gt;property = 'value'; ) vs. array index style ($object['property'] = 'value'; ).</p>

<p>If you set in array style, you can get in array or object style.</p>

<p>If you set in object style, you cannot get in array style, and the object does not handle the assigned value correctly.</p>

